data.description: This 4-bedroom, 2.5 bath home is a gem built in 2019. It boasts an open concept with high ceilings, crown molding, and a split floor plan. The kitchen is stunning with Corian counters, a large island, and an oversized walk-in pantry with a sliding barn door. The tiled backsplash, stainless appliances, gas cooktop, and custom cabinets add a touch of luxury. The wood look tiled flooring throughout the hall, bathrooms, entryway, kitchen, living room, and laundry room is both stylish and practical. The master suite is a dream with a whirlpool tub, crown molding and a large walk-in closet that conveniently connects to the laundry room.  This home is also equipped with newly installed solar panels for additional energy savings!
